title: DUCT TAPE SAVES THE DAY - Broken Fishing Rod!  Tenkara Fly Fishing For Westslope Cutthroat Trout.

media:group.media:title: DUCT TAPE SAVES THE DAY - Broken Fishing Rod!  Tenkara Fly Fishing For Westslope Cutthroat Trout.
media:group.media:description: In this video I fly fish for the elusive Westslope Cutthroat Trout in Oregon on Strawberry Creek. Even Though I broke my fishing rod I still had a great time catching these beautiful native fish.
